Oh Obi One Anthony Boiurdain I have once again followed in your footsteps, braved the lines, and supped at the source of all things good about chicken and rice. Singapore's National obsession is best done here . This amazingly simple, but yet complex dish, burst full of robust chicken flavor. It has all been said before, only for those who have not been to Singapore, you cannot understand it until you have made your way to Singapore.. And in the world of chicken and rice and the lines that follow, as Yoda says, "There is no try, only do."